---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof for Cleaning Services — Reviews & Testimonials That Book More Clients | SocialProof" description="Cleaning services: turn happy clients into booked jobs with automated testimonials. SocialProof collects 5-star reviews and displays them where prospects make decisions.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Cleaning Services
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Someone is about to let you into their home. The only thing standing between "browsing" and "booking" is trust. SocialProof helps cleaning services, house cleaners, and maid services collect and display the testimonials that turn website visitors into recurring clients.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Trust is the only barrier to booking</h2>
      <p>Cleaning services have a unique challenge: clients need to trust you with their home, their valuables, and their family's daily environment. A Google listing with no reviews or an empty website testimonials section sends every prospect to your competitor — even if your work is excellent.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">SocialProof makes it dead simple to collect written testimonials from your happy recurring clients and show them prominently on your booking page, homepage, and service pages.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The testimonials that convert cleaning prospects</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> "They've never missed an appointment in 2 years. Not once."</li>
        <li><strong>Trustworthiness:</strong> "We gave them a key and never thought twice about it."</li>
        <li><strong>Thoroughness:</strong> "Got in corners my previous cleaner hadn't touched in months."</li>
        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> "They texted when they arrived and when they finished. Love that."</li>
        <li><strong>Results:</strong> "House smells amazing. I come home to a completely different space."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How it works for your cleaning business</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your booking page and homepage — takes about 10 minutes, no coding needed.</li>
        <li><strong>After every clean</strong> (or every few cleans for recurring clients), send the simple collection link via text or email.</li>
        <li><strong>Approve and publish</strong> testimonials with one click — or enable auto-publish for trusted regulars.</li>
        <li><strong>New visitors see real clients</strong> vouching for your reliability before they've even spoken to you.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for every cleaning business model</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Residential house cleaning (recurring & one-time)</li>
        <li>Move-in / move-out deep cleans</li>
        <li>Airbnb & short-term rental turnovers</li>
        <li>Post-construction cleanup</li>
        <li>Commercial office cleaning</li>
        <li>Specialty cleaning (carpets, windows, upholstery)</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #bbf7d0;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;color:#166534;">
          "I added SocialProof to my booking page and within a month I had 18 testimonials showing. My conversion rate went up noticeably — people who used to just 'check prices' started actually booking."
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#14532d;">— Owner, residential cleaning service</p>
      </div>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Free to start</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for 1 active widget. That's enough to put testimonials on your booking page and start converting more visitors. No credit card required to get started.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <a href="/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#2563eb;color:white;padding:0.85rem 2.2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
          Get started free
        </a>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#888;">Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

